query:
UPDATE servers
            SET
                owner_id = $1, egg_id = $2, external_id = $3,
                name = $4, description = $5, cpu = $6, memory = $7,
                swap = $8, disk = $9, io_weight = $10, pinned_cpus = $11,
                startup = $12, image = $13, timezone = $14, allocation_limit = $15,
                backup_limit = $16, database_limit = $17
            WHERE id = $18
